replies.body:
I'd like to know why none of those changes you're looking into ever made it onto the PBE. It really doesn't shine a good light on your efforts, to be honest. **All we see from your team are promises but no actions, this has been going on for a LONG time already.** 

What happened to all those suggestions you recieved those past weeks? Have you even looked into reverting the damage on her Q while adding a damage-reduction to creeps? There are plenty more of those ideas and yet **you haven't taken any of them seriously** by the look of things.

I've been playing Soraka on my main hundreds of times already which is why I consider myself a dedicated Soraka player who has grown very fond of this champion. Seeing her reduced to be the focus of ongoing ridicule did truly upset me. **When will you realize that we don't want to wait for several months just to play our favorite goat again?** {{champion:16}}
